comments: Suggs (ORL) turns to roll and marginal contact occurs with Little (POR) as Little (POR) goes under the pick.
Lillard (POR) defends Banchero's (ORL) drive to the basket and marginal contact occurs that does not affect his SQBR.
Lillard (POR) places his forearm to Banchero's (ORL) front during his drive to the basket and marginal body contact occurs during his driving shot attempt.
Wagner (ORL) brings his arm toward Lillard's (POR) path and marginal contact occurs during Lillard's (POR) drive.
Wagner (ORL) places his forearm to Lillard's (POR) side after Lillard gathers the rebound and marginal contact occurs.
Banchero (ORL) legally contests Lillard's (POR) jump shot attempt.
Fultz (ORL) and Eubanks (POR) engage and immediately disengage as marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Wagner (ORL) and Grant (POR) come together in pursuit of the loose ball and marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Grant (POR) initiates contact with Wagner's (ORL) arm, which affects his play at the basket.
Banchero (ORL) moves alongside of Lillard's (POR) path to the basket and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Eubanks (POR) briefly places his hand to Fultz's (ORL) front during his driving shot attempt.
Eubanks (POR) establishes himself in Fultz's (ORL) path and does not deliver contact.
Banchero (ORL) legally contests Little's (POR) jump shot attempt.
Wagner (ORL) slightly extends his arms outside of his body frame and does not deliver contact to Thybulle (POR) during the screen.
Wagner (ORL) establishes himself in Reddish's (POR) path and gives him a step to avoid the contact.
Lillard (POR) moves laterally into Wagner's (ORL) path and initiates body contact that affects Wagner's (ORL) SQBR during the drive.
Fultz (ORL) and Lillard (POR) engage and disengage with one another and marginal contact occurs off-ball.
Reddish (POR) establishes himself in Fultz's (ORL) path and does not deliver contact.
Houstan (ORL) initiates contact with Lillard's (POR) arm, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Grant (POR) and Houstan (ORL) engage and disengage with one another and marginal contact occurs off-ball.
Reddish (POR) commits a take foul on Fultz (ORL).
Suggs (ORL) and Lillard (POR) engage and disengage with one another and marginal contact occurs off-ball.
Banchero (ORL) commits a take foul on Grant (POR).
Grant (POR) commits a take foul on Banchero (ORL).
Suggs (ORL) falls and makes marginal contact to Lillard's (POR) lower body as he gathers the entry pass.
Houstan (ORL) commits a take foul on Lillard (POR).
Reddish (POR) reaches in and initiates contact to Banchero's (ORL) body that affects his SQBR.  The contact occurs prior to Banchero's gather and a non-shooting foul should be called.
